{"tid":632231,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黃金時期既香港電影","createTime":"2018-04-17T07:53:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-17T09:49:51.000Z","uid":82917,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8fa6e7eae2b9f8a5eff81484ac63b1ee50b5dab4","tid":632231,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T07:53:24.000Z","msg":"點解我地係咁拎返廿年前黃金時代既港產片打飛機？<br />\n本土味既電影沒落得太快<br />\n廿年咋 點解退步成咁？<br />\n琴晚個頒獎禮 愈睇愈心酸<br />\n黃秋生講個番說話竟然一個拍手支持佢既人都冇<br />\n幾時變得咁唔敢言？<br />\n我地距離變成香港市不遠了。。<br />\n回不去了。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好想生係個個輝煌既年代<br />\n可以感受下個個都崇港個份自豪感<br />\n不朽香江名句。。。。。<br />\n點解咁遲先出世。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又要叫春了。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n我愛香港電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我愛舊時香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a5033c2063ba1c065d719d339b77275ece0468e","tid":632231,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T07:53:42.000Z","msg":"好心酸。。。。"},{"pid":"178d3c9dca2d4f2832456216a0764d73bc9a332c","tid":632231,"uid":82917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T07:54:15.000Z","msg":"睇住而家啲00後祟韓祟強 唔知可以講咩了"},{"pid":"c741eeab490d28e59b6c79ed9136c155b581122d","tid":632231,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T07:54:32.000Z","msg":"會唔會幾年後就冇人識講廣東話。。。"},{"pid":"e2054efac8faad2fbb145527347560df5095584b","tid":632231,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T07:54:48.000Z","msg":"點解會咁？"},{"pid":"5544e4b477715a0f53e00dbfa75b441a6b83f571","tid":632231,"uid":82917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T07:55:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asset